{"data":[{"id":560461710,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560461710","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-1e0cdf5e487ef87fdcb501e3dbfc89c9_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545839596,"updated_time":1546068718,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":122,"comment_count":40,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e12.29更新：\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e偶然在网上发现了科学出版社2011年出版的《哥德巴赫猜想》（第二版，潘承洞、潘承彪著\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e）的试读章节链接。感兴趣的可以点击\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.ecsponline.com/yz/B64EDB42D69214CEEB63DA63C7A996100000.pdf\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e这个链接\u003c/a\u003e下载。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e虽然只有引言，但恕我直言，贵乎上能完全读懂引言的人可能不超过【数据删除】个。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有志于研究哥猜者可以去某宝或某东购买全书，并不算太贵。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e况且，再次恕我直言，\u003cb\u003e真正\u003c/b\u003e有能力研究哥猜的人应该都能够接触到图书馆。至少我查了敝校的图书馆，还是有几本的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a31240b415dd25db97fc13c124076529_b.jpg\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1748\" data-rawheight=\"745\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a31240b415dd25db97fc13c124076529_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1748\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a31240b415dd25db97fc13c124076529_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1748'%20height='745'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1748\" data-rawheight=\"745\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a31240b415dd25db97fc13c124076529_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1748\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a31240b415dd25db97fc13c124076529_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a31240b415dd25db97fc13c124076529_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e就是这本书\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e千万要注意\u003c/b\u003e不要买到徐迟所著的那个同名报（ji）告（tang）文学。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e今天哥猜能成为民科聚集地，不可谓没有上面那本报告文学的“功劳”呢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e------------------12.29分割线------------------\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在知乎上发表……您会吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f956d2cf9e33c9ae796fcc80cade6ee9_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"924\" data-rawheight=\"716\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f956d2cf9e33c9ae796fcc80cade6ee9_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"924\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f956d2cf9e33c9ae796fcc80cade6ee9_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='924'%20height='716'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"924\" data-rawheight=\"716\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f956d2cf9e33c9ae796fcc80cade6ee9_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"924\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f956d2cf9e33c9ae796fcc80cade6ee9_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f956d2cf9e33c9ae796fcc80cade6ee9_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果不会的话，还有4天，学会Latex公式语法足够了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e学会Latex语法之后，在数学方面的顶级期刊发文章也是没问题的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果您说您的证明“根本用不到这些需要用公式编辑器才能打出来的玩意”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对不起\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e慢走不送\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e-----------12.27更新分割线-----------\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这位仁兄似乎开了个叫“数学”的专栏……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e估计证明方法就会发在里面吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e居然有些期待呢（x\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（1）如果半年后他真的能进入大学学习数学，这个专栏可能会成为一个能够交流数学（*真正的数学）的地方。如果真的有那一天，希望大家都忘记他当年年轻气盛时曾经声称证明了哥猜吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e （2）如果不然，那里想必要变成民科理论聚集地了。真是可怕。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e衷心希望最后结果（1）成立。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如下为陈景润论文里的一个公式。我当然完全看不懂\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e但我至少没有声称自己证明了哥猜\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cnotag%5Csum_%7BD%3Cq%5Cleqslant+Q%7D%5E%7B%7D%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B%5Cvarphi+%28q%29%7D%7B%5C+%7D+%7B%5Csum_%7B%7B%5Cchi%7D_q%7D%5E%7B%7D%7D%5E%7B%5Cast+%7D%7B%5Cleft+%7C+%5Csum_%7Bn%3DM%2B1%7D%5E%7BM%2BN%7D+a_n+%7B%5Cchi%7D_%7Bq%7D%28n%29%5Cright+%7C%7D%5E%7B2%7D%5Cleqslant+%5Csum_%7Bi%3D0%7D%5E%7Bh%7D%5Cleft+%28%5Csum_%7B2%5EiD%3Cq%5Cleqslant+2%5E%7Bi%2B1%7DD%7D%5E%7B%7D%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B%5Cvarphi+%28q%29%7D%7B%5Csum_%7B%7B%5Cchi%7D_q%7D%5E%7B%7D%7D%5E%7B%5Cast+%7D%7B%5Cleft+%7C+%5Csum_%7Bn%3DM%2B1%7D%5E%7BM%2BN%7D+a_n+%7B%5Cchi%7D_%7Bq%7D%28n%29%5Cright+%7C%7D%5E%7B2%7D%5Cright+%29%5C%5C+%5Cnotag%5Cleqslant+%7B%7D+%5Csum_%7Bi%3D0%7D%5E%7Bh%7D%5Cleft+%28%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B2%5EiD%7D%5Cright+%29%5Cleft+%28%5Csum_%7B2%5EiD%3Cq%5Cleqslant+2%5E%7Bi%2B1%7DD%7D%5E%7B%7D%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B%5Cvarphi+%28q%29%7D%7B%5Csum_%7B%7B%5Cchi%7D_q%7D%5E%7B%7D%7D%5E%7B%5C